<h2>The Physical Desk</h2>
<figure class="img-figure"><div class="img-wrapper" data-tooltip="Minimal Workspace Setup by Carl Barenbrug" style="padding-bottom: 150%"><img alt="Minimal Workspace Setup by Carl Barenbrug" class="img" loading="lazy" src="https://carlbarenbrug.com/media/pages/blog/workspace-revisited/609f9b9136-1690029230/workspace.jpg"></div></figure>
