            <description><![CDATA[<p>For the longest time, I’ve shared my work through blog posts or social media, rather than having a typical portfolio. But I’ve decided it’s time to pull together a more cohesive collection of my work, focusing on product design and creative direction. My projects are usually long-term endeavours. Although I'm happy to make time for the occasional freelance project, I tend to focus my attention on work I can iterate, refine, and evolve over time.</p>
