            <description><![CDATA[<p>I think it's been about three years since I last updated my desk setup. But I recently made some changes, which I'd like to share with you. The overall dark vibe of my previous setup has remained, but I've upgraded a few elements. See my <a href="https://carlbarenbrug.com/blog/workspace-revisited-2022">2022 workspace setup</a> if you're curious.</p>
